sections.Trivia:
- The suspects' names come from "gemstones"[1]:
Juri Shinkai (新海 樹梨) comes from pearls (真珠 ,shinju?) ;
Shogo Masui (増井 祥吾) comes from crystal (水晶 ,suishō?) ;
Isao Hisumi (日住 勲) comes from jade (翡翠 ,hisui?).
